{"tid":2206500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎耀祥成日問人哋有幾多個十年，涉嫌煽惑他人睇中共禁片","createTime":"2020-09-17T13:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T13:37:01.000Z","uid":229502,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38f6fd053530225e4fe94c0e9c1074d181efda95","tid":2206500,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUdo8KA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUdo8KA.png&h=c9e31063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n TVB染黃真係好嚴重!! 除咗劇組，原來連偽人黎耀祥都係黃屍，記者之前問佢點睇国安法，佢竟然答冇乜留意!? 諗諗吓<strong><span class=\"red\">佢成日重提老掉牙嘅「人生有幾多個十年」，不斷提及祖国禁片，想食盡兩家茶禮賺人仔?</span></strong> 我呸！我唔會再睇YCTVB，更加唔會睇你套雙祥見! <strong><span class=\"red\">屌你老味嬲嬲地, 派埋嬲比你啲廣告商<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZOgKyF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZOgKyF.jpg&h=31a0b041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>十年？你終於露出狐狸尾巴！</strong></span><br />\n <p class=\"center\">【每日任務@ 17 Sep】 💎 正官庄 💎 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ckjhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fckjhk%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=fbce5fd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ckjhk/</a> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6ZLCca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6ZLCca.png&h=00de224b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p> 正官庄係三料廣告商，首先呢兩年都有喺TVB賣廣告；第二搵咗戲裡戲外都跋扈囂張嘅黎耀祥（A.K.A.韓信）嚟代言；第三喺Big Big Shop寄賣。 黎耀祥金句： 「經常鬧TVB的人，我覺得沒有良心」、「我真係唔信你細個無睇過電視，到今時今日大個，巴閉喇，讀咗書喇，知識分子搵到錢喇，中產喇，飲杯咖啡睇法國電影喇，就話呢啲（劇集）好膠喇」 ============================================ [quote]<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【抵制 TVB戰線】</span></span></strong> Follow 抵制TVB戰線，每日派嬲，對方廣告費就億億聲咁跌！ <span class=\"x-large\"> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=adae388c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a> </span></p>"},{"pid":"bdf8f64501ec2a84546c3ae63986951bb2d644c6","tid":2206500,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5950b1e655ad40cb7b260244f48c2a2cc1e9d8","tid":2206500,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"OMG<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc87e9f52dc3c635d547e6de12a89dc19d2a643","tid":2206500,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e5fb9c9c57d4bd3e69ed964145ff993a7512e5","tid":2206500,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5950b1e655ad40cb7b260244f48c2a2cc1e9d8","tid":2206500,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"OMG<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62719620d8eb39e25ab8631704d93ea4bb56951","tid":2206500,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdf8f64501ec2a84546c3ae63986951bb2d644c6","tid":2206500,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face